\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marcus opened his eyes once again, satisfied that his mana pool was back to full capacity and he was ready for whatever came next. It was only as he stood up and stretched that it finally occurred to him that he last slept more than 24 hours ago, before the second evaluation began. He also hadn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t had any food or water for more than 60 hours now. He checked the time remaining until the next evaluation and his resource pools before pursuing the thought further.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 <$Scr_Ps::0>Rest period duration remaining 0:19:59}
