\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93So, how is it that I haven\u8217\'92t slept in more than 24 hours and haven\u8217\'92t needed to eat or drink in more than three days, yet I feel fine and don\u8217\'92t see any detrimental effects?\u8221\'94 He asked. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Once a sapient has crossed the first mana compression threshold, their body adapts to use mana as its primary fuel source instead of requiring sustenance,\u8221\'94 she answered with a smile. \u8220\'93You will only ever experience hunger or thirst if you are in a low mana area that is incapable of sustaining your core. As for sleep, meditation is an adequate substitute for sleep, capable of sustaining your mind for several days without needing actual sleep. so long as your mental energy is not overly depleted.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Mental energy? What do you mean?\u8221\'94 He was quite positive there was no such thing on his status screen.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Mental energy is a combination of stamina and soul stability. While not directly tracked by the System, it is a measure of your ability to be alert, aware and focused on a task. As it wanes, you will begin to feel mentally fatigued. Only actual sleep will restore your mental energy.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93So I\u8217\'92m more likely to need sleep after intense mental activity, whereas restoring the body is a lot easier and can be accomplished with meditation?\u8221\'94 He raised an eyebrow at the how backward that seemed.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Essentially yes,\u8221\'94 she agreed, \u8220\'93though that is an oversimplification. Even without intense mental activity, you will eventually run low on mental energy and require actual sleep. You simply won\u8217\'92t require it nearly so often as you once did.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Huh, that\u8217\'92s good to know.\u8221\'94 Marcus nodded slightly as he considered it. \u8220\'93It will have a helluva an impact on civilization as a whole though.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
