\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 You have earned the title \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8216\'91Professional Problem Solver\u8217\'92. Title grants +3 each to Intelligence and Wisdom.<!$Scr_Ps::0>}
